WEBVTT

00:00:00.340 --> 00:00:01.340
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

00:00:01.410 --> 00:00:03.410
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:05.180
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:34.410
(Episode 6)

00:00:35.470 --> 00:00:36.470
Here.

00:00:41.650 --> 00:00:44.120
Ta-da. Happy birthday, Min Jun.

00:00:48.290 --> 00:00:50.320
Happy birthday to you too,
Baek Jin Ju.

00:00:53.690 --> 00:00:54.690
Here you go.

00:00:56.290 --> 00:00:57.300
Thanks.

00:01:00.830 --> 00:01:02.500
That's a great photo.

00:01:02.800 --> 00:01:04.400
- Nice, right?
- Yes.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:07.470
- This turned out great.
- Right?

00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:10.040
Why don't we take one together?

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:12.980
One, two, three.

00:01:15.050 --> 00:01:16.080
It snapped on two.

00:01:17.580 --> 00:01:20.490
- Hey!
- Unbelievable.

00:01:29.490 --> 00:01:30.800
Watch it, will you?

00:01:31.860 --> 00:01:33.030
I could've gotten hurt.

00:01:33.870 --> 00:01:35.530
Are your eyes just for show?

00:01:39.070 --> 00:01:40.070
What's with her?

00:01:40.670 --> 00:01:42.340
Why'd you only get yourself
in the picture?

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:47.580
It really is Park Min Jun.

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:50.650
- Is it the angle?
- I guess so.

00:01:51.550 --> 00:01:54.020
I didn't know Park Min Jun
could make a face like that.

00:01:56.650 --> 00:01:59.320
A guy who's so incredibly boring...

00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:01.130
has a girlfriend?

00:02:09.670 --> 00:02:14.240
The design is very simple,
yet it maintains an air of elegance.

00:02:15.740 --> 00:02:16.740
Please, take your time with it.

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.240
- Director Kim.
- Gosh, welcome.

00:02:19.310 --> 00:02:20.510
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:02:20.510 --> 00:02:23.080
- The designs today are gorgeous.
- Thank you.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:29.450
- I want to buy everything.
- It's already sold out.

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:30.520
They're so beautiful.

00:02:31.290 --> 00:02:33.530
- I'd love one.
- I have to have it.

00:02:33.660 --> 00:02:36.430
I have prepared some loose diamonds
for you here.

00:02:36.860 --> 00:02:39.900
The theme of this VIP
collection event...

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:41.800
is "Only One."

00:02:42.230 --> 00:02:44.740
From design to craftsmanship,

00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:46.200
tailored to your needs and taste,

00:02:46.270 --> 00:02:48.370
we will be providing...

00:02:48.370 --> 00:02:49.510
a completely customized service.

00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:53.380
But isn't jewelry
all about the design?

00:02:53.380 --> 00:02:54.550
This clearly lacks it.

00:02:54.980 --> 00:02:56.310
Why should I buy it
on trust alone...

00:02:56.310 --> 00:02:57.680
when it's not well crafted?

00:02:57.780 --> 00:02:59.620
Then trust my reputation.

00:03:00.350 --> 00:03:03.350
If our highly respected
AD Appraisal Report...

00:03:03.350 --> 00:03:04.890
also bears my name,

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:07.130
wouldn't that be value enough?

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:10.660
That's true.
Director Kim's name is a brand.

00:03:11.060 --> 00:03:13.030
AD Appraisals' credibility...

00:03:13.030 --> 00:03:15.800
is built
on Director Kim's appraisals.

00:03:16.670 --> 00:03:20.270
The AD Appraisal Report is even
recognized internationally now.

00:03:21.370 --> 00:03:23.940
This collection,
which I'm staking my name on,

00:03:24.040 --> 00:03:25.880
is offered with terms
rarely found...

00:03:25.880 --> 00:03:27.480
outside an event like this.

00:03:28.810 --> 00:03:29.810
Let's go.

00:03:37.990 --> 00:03:39.320
Don't let her get to you, Ms. Kim.

00:03:40.160 --> 00:03:42.760
Apparently,
her husband took a mistress.

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:47.030
Since you're rumored to be
Chairman Park's mistress,

00:03:47.300 --> 00:03:48.770
she's just taking it out on you.

00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:52.400
Anyway,
Chairman Park is so shortsighted.

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:54.840
AD Appraisals
and the jewelry business...

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:56.870
took off because of you,

00:03:56.940 --> 00:03:59.040
and he used that success
to build a conglomerate.

00:03:59.410 --> 00:04:01.580
I don't understand why he lets you
be treated like a mistress.

00:04:02.710 --> 00:04:04.820
Instead of focusing only on jewelry,

00:04:04.820 --> 00:04:07.090
you should think about Adele Group
as a whole.

00:04:08.150 --> 00:04:09.750
I heard your son
is a senior in college.

00:04:10.590 --> 00:04:12.490
So isn't the succession war
about to begin?

00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:15.060
The chairman's wife is networking...

00:04:15.060 --> 00:04:16.830
with the wives
of political and business leaders,

00:04:16.890 --> 00:04:19.100
bringing up potential marriage prospects
for her son.

00:04:19.730 --> 00:04:21.870
You need to start preparing too.

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.900
Have you heard of Ihwachae?

00:04:27.740 --> 00:04:28.740
I hear they arrange marriages...

00:04:28.740 --> 00:04:30.710
for the political
and business elite.

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:33.510
It's also invitation-only.

00:04:38.050 --> 00:04:40.050
Mrs. Han from Ihwachae
asked me to give this to you.

00:04:40.550 --> 00:04:41.550
Me?

00:04:41.890 --> 00:04:43.520
Even if you don't marry him off now,

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:45.120
you should still get a consultation.

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:47.690
It can't hurt to get
to know Mrs. Han,

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:51.700
and it's a good way to get under
the chairman's wife's skin.

00:05:05.140 --> 00:05:08.180
Was she trying to annoy you
or actually help?

00:05:09.150 --> 00:05:10.780
I think she just wants a show.

00:05:11.080 --> 00:05:12.080
What show?

00:05:12.620 --> 00:05:13.620
A showdown.

00:05:14.950 --> 00:05:15.950
That's cold.

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:19.890
Provoking someone
who's fought for 20 years?

00:05:41.850 --> 00:05:43.050
It's been tampered with.

00:05:50.290 --> 00:05:51.790
(Baby's Meal, Omega 1)

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:54.930
To protect Min Jun,

00:05:55.660 --> 00:05:57.600
I have to stay on guard
at all times.

00:05:58.460 --> 00:06:02.230
("Finding the Shadow")

00:06:03.800 --> 00:06:06.770
("Gemstone Appraisal
and Identification Theory")

00:06:12.610 --> 00:06:14.050
To take over Adele Group,

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:16.810
I'll need a specialty of my own.

00:06:23.350 --> 00:06:24.360
Listen.

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:27.360
A mistress should know her place
and stick to powdering her nose.

00:06:27.830 --> 00:06:29.560
What's she doing
meddling in men's business?

00:06:30.360 --> 00:06:33.970
I've been running AD Appraisals
just fine!

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:41.340
Are the institute's diamonds
getting any respect in the market?

00:06:43.140 --> 00:06:45.640
Carat, color, clarity, and cut.

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:48.980
The results in each of these areas
are being falsified.

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:51.180
And it's not just the diamonds
from AD Appraisals.

00:06:51.720 --> 00:06:54.250
Even Adele Jewelry's gemstones...

00:06:54.250 --> 00:06:55.650
are losing their credibility.

00:06:57.790 --> 00:06:59.260
From now on,

00:06:59.660 --> 00:07:01.230
I will take charge,
from the institute...

00:07:01.990 --> 00:07:03.690
to quality control at Adele Jewelry.

00:07:04.700 --> 00:07:06.430
I will oversee
everything meticulously.

00:07:12.070 --> 00:07:13.100
Are you out of your mind?

00:07:16.070 --> 00:07:18.940
Min Jun's mom?
What do you think you're doing?

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:21.250
You can't say a word to my face,

00:07:22.150 --> 00:07:24.050
but you hurt my son like this
behind my back?

00:07:25.820 --> 00:07:26.820
(Park Min Jun,
Illegitimate, Disgusting)

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:28.850
(Illegitimate, A disgrace,
Mom says he's disgusting, Just die)

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:35.090
Why make such a big deal
out of kids' jokes?

00:07:36.090 --> 00:07:39.300
You think crushing a child's spirit
is a joke?

00:07:41.530 --> 00:07:43.630
If you ever hurt my son again,

00:07:44.770 --> 00:07:47.240
you'll see what my crazy
is capable of.

00:07:57.980 --> 00:08:00.350
She probably thinks your only battle
was with Oh Jung Ran.

00:08:00.820 --> 00:08:02.890
As a gem appraiser
and as Min Jun's mother,

00:08:03.150 --> 00:08:04.920
if she knew
how hard you've had to fight,

00:08:05.460 --> 00:08:07.860
she wouldn't dare turn you
into a spectacle for her amusement.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:10.260
Who cares what other people say?

00:08:11.060 --> 00:08:12.430
As long as it helps our cause,

00:08:13.200 --> 00:08:14.670
I don't mind being turned
into a spectacle.

00:08:14.830 --> 00:08:15.830
No way.

00:08:16.030 --> 00:08:18.040
Oh Jung Ran should be
the one humiliated.

00:08:18.970 --> 00:08:19.970
Just you wait.

00:08:20.910 --> 00:08:23.710
What I've set in motion
should be starting right about now.

00:08:24.810 --> 00:08:28.410
I doubt she'll be welcomed
by the other society wives now.

00:08:34.520 --> 00:08:37.150
Hey, what did you just say?

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:44.030
That there are two wives
at Adele Group?

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:47.130
How dare you use that title
for that common trash?

00:08:47.430 --> 00:08:48.430
I'm sorry.

00:08:48.430 --> 00:08:50.640
I was just repeating
what the other ladies said.

00:08:50.700 --> 00:08:51.700
The others?

00:08:54.110 --> 00:08:55.740
What did the other ladies say?

00:08:56.310 --> 00:08:57.310
Well,

00:08:57.940 --> 00:08:59.880
they said you just run a gallery...

00:08:59.880 --> 00:09:02.180
and do the chairman's bidding,

00:09:02.280 --> 00:09:03.510
while Director Kim...

00:09:03.710 --> 00:09:07.550
is a gemologist
with a thriving jewelry business.

00:09:07.620 --> 00:09:08.820
His bidding?

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:13.660
Do you have any idea
how important my errands are?

00:09:14.530 --> 00:09:18.060
They even said Director Kim's son
will inherit Adele Group.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:19.960
So if you want to marry
into the family,

00:09:19.960 --> 00:09:21.700
her son is your best bet.

00:09:22.630 --> 00:09:25.800
Hey, my son is the rightful heir
to the Adele family.

00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:28.110
How dare you even let those words
pass your lips?

00:09:28.170 --> 00:09:31.240
I'm so sorry.
I was just saying what I heard...

00:09:31.380 --> 00:09:33.440
Why would you repeat
all the details?

00:09:33.440 --> 00:09:35.080
You should've known better.

00:09:35.150 --> 00:09:36.650
You dare challenge
my son's position?

00:09:37.150 --> 00:09:39.680
Do you know who you're messing with?

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:41.650
Do I look like a pushover to you?

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:42.920
Ma'am, please!

00:09:43.190 --> 00:09:45.290
You think
I'm going to let this slide?

00:09:45.890 --> 00:09:47.530
How dare you?

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:53.930
I thought I warned you clearly.

00:09:54.700 --> 00:09:55.930
I told you to stay out of it,

00:09:55.930 --> 00:09:58.370
since marriage and succession
are my call.

00:09:59.300 --> 00:10:02.310
But you just had to stir up trouble,

00:10:02.510 --> 00:10:03.770
get into a hair pulling fight,

00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:05.480
and have the whole thing
caught on video.

00:10:06.240 --> 00:10:09.280
They're the ones
who disrespected our Hyun Jun first.

00:10:10.180 --> 00:10:11.420
How could I just stand by...

00:10:11.420 --> 00:10:13.180
and let them tarnish
Hyun Jun's name?

00:10:14.020 --> 00:10:16.720
So you decided to tarnish
Adele Group's name instead?

00:10:18.560 --> 00:10:20.660
While you've been causing trouble,

00:10:20.660 --> 00:10:23.160
do you have any idea
how much money Kim Myung Hui made...

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:25.600
running the jewelry business?

00:10:27.370 --> 00:10:29.230
Why do you always compare me
to that trash?

00:10:30.130 --> 00:10:33.500
I run Adele Gallery
and line your pockets.

00:10:33.770 --> 00:10:34.910
I'm the one...

00:10:34.910 --> 00:10:37.240
who sets up and launders
your slush fund.

00:10:40.040 --> 00:10:41.180
Manager Kang!

00:10:44.850 --> 00:10:45.880
Yes, sir.

00:10:48.350 --> 00:10:49.750
Have Butler Ok...

00:10:49.950 --> 00:10:52.190
move Jung Ran's things
from our bedroom to the annex.

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:56.090
- Again?
- And clear out Hyun Jun's room too!

00:10:56.860 --> 00:10:58.200
Honey, please.

00:10:58.530 --> 00:11:00.930
I'm the master of Adele Group.

00:11:01.800 --> 00:11:03.330
If you're going to defy me,

00:11:03.330 --> 00:11:05.470
you'd better be prepared.

00:11:23.350 --> 00:11:24.520
Mrs. Ok!

00:11:25.820 --> 00:11:27.090
You're back, ma'am.

00:11:28.230 --> 00:11:29.360
There you go again.

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:31.300
Didn't I tell you not to smile?

00:11:31.700 --> 00:11:34.300
Can't you at least not smirk
when I'm being kicked out?

00:11:35.300 --> 00:11:37.030
There you go again,
misunderstanding me.

00:11:37.130 --> 00:11:38.500
I told you before,

00:11:38.500 --> 00:11:41.240
I just have
a naturally smiling face.

00:11:41.310 --> 00:11:42.870
You know
I have the same expression...

00:11:42.870 --> 00:11:45.240
whether I'm angry or even swearing.

00:11:45.640 --> 00:11:48.280
It breaks my heart
that you're being moved...

00:11:48.280 --> 00:11:49.510
to the annex,

00:11:49.580 --> 00:11:51.080
but what can I do?

00:11:51.080 --> 00:11:53.950
I can't help my expression.

00:11:54.890 --> 00:11:58.690
It's exhausting for me, too,
always looking like this.

00:12:02.190 --> 00:12:04.600
She's totally faking it. I can tell.

00:12:05.460 --> 00:12:09.300
He just had to hire
the strangest looking butler. Darn.

00:12:24.080 --> 00:12:25.480
Must be nice for you.

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:26.820
While Hyun Jun has to follow me...

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:29.050
back and forth
between the main house and the annex,

00:12:29.050 --> 00:12:30.120
you and your mother...

00:12:30.120 --> 00:12:32.490
get to stay comfortably right here.

00:12:35.630 --> 00:12:36.630
You.

00:12:37.360 --> 00:12:40.060
Don't underestimate us
just because we're in the annex.

00:12:40.460 --> 00:12:43.230
Hyun Jun is the one and only heir
to Adele Group.

00:12:43.800 --> 00:12:46.640
If you ever think
about challenging his position,

00:12:47.540 --> 00:12:50.910
I will tear you and your mother
to shreds.

00:12:51.410 --> 00:12:52.410
Got it?

00:12:55.750 --> 00:12:57.210
There it is again.

00:12:57.410 --> 00:13:00.150
Didn't I tell you
I hate that look in your eyes?

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:02.850
How dare you look me in the eye?

00:13:02.850 --> 00:13:04.360
You'd rather he glare at you?

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:09.830
You'd just find a reason
to yell at him for that, too.

00:13:10.060 --> 00:13:11.800
- You.
- Ms. Oh.

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:14.830
Looks like you got kicked out again
for causing trouble.

00:13:15.270 --> 00:13:17.470
Don't take it out on him.
Just get moving.

00:13:17.540 --> 00:13:20.370
The annex!
It'll be a nice change of scenery.

00:13:21.270 --> 00:13:22.470
Come on, let's go.

00:13:22.710 --> 00:13:25.410
- Come on, let's go.
- Let go of me.

00:13:27.180 --> 00:13:29.610
- Let's get going.
- Seriously, stop it.

00:13:39.290 --> 00:13:40.860
- For crying out loud!
- In you go.

00:13:42.490 --> 00:13:45.100
Whose side are you on anyway?

00:13:45.300 --> 00:13:46.900
Yours, Mom.

00:13:47.100 --> 00:13:48.100
What?

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:51.400
Ms. Oh, bullying nice people
brings bad karma.

00:13:51.870 --> 00:13:54.670
Thanks to me,
you won't be punished too harshly.

00:13:54.740 --> 00:13:57.710
A nice person? Get a grip.

00:13:58.440 --> 00:14:01.410
He's a snake
trying to take your place as heir.

00:14:01.550 --> 00:14:04.010
What will you do
when he steals your birthright?

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:06.620
Isn't that better
than ruining my entire life over it?

00:14:06.920 --> 00:14:08.020
Park Hyun Jun.

00:14:08.090 --> 00:14:10.320
Mom, you're the one who said...

00:14:10.320 --> 00:14:12.560
I did my part by being born a son.

00:14:12.620 --> 00:14:15.030
Why expect so much from someone
who's already done his job?

00:14:15.090 --> 00:14:16.530
Am I doing this for myself?

00:14:16.530 --> 00:14:18.460
- This is all for your own good.
- Don't...

00:14:18.460 --> 00:14:19.830
look out for me.

00:14:19.830 --> 00:14:22.030
It's every man for himself.

00:14:22.100 --> 00:14:23.530
My way or nothing.

00:14:23.970 --> 00:14:25.500
Every what for himself?

00:14:27.840 --> 00:14:29.370
You live your life,
and I'll live mine.

00:14:29.640 --> 00:14:33.180
And stop thinking of us
as a two-for-one deal.

00:14:33.940 --> 00:14:37.480
You go your way, and I'll go mine.

00:14:39.420 --> 00:14:41.790
Ms. Oh, you're going to catch flies.

00:14:42.450 --> 00:14:44.860
Then, I'm off to enjoy my life.

00:14:46.920 --> 00:14:49.360
- Hyun Jun, you're back from school.
- I'm heading back out!

00:14:50.360 --> 00:14:52.360
Unbelievable!

00:14:53.030 --> 00:14:55.500
This is so frustrating.

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:58.100
Seriously, who does he take after?

00:14:58.870 --> 00:15:00.370
What do you mean?

00:15:00.370 --> 00:15:02.470
What's wrong with our Hyun Jun?

00:15:03.110 --> 00:15:05.040
He says he's not interested.

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:07.910
He has no interest
in being the heir.

00:15:07.910 --> 00:15:09.650
He's going to walk away
from Adele Group...

00:15:09.650 --> 00:15:11.350
and his entire future there.

00:15:11.420 --> 00:15:14.720
That's for you to take care of.

00:15:16.650 --> 00:15:18.190
Easy for you to say.

00:15:18.590 --> 00:15:19.690
The chairman...

00:15:19.690 --> 00:15:22.360
has turned Hyun Jun's room upside down
countless times,

00:15:22.490 --> 00:15:25.630
but he's never once laid a finger
on Min Jun's.

00:15:25.700 --> 00:15:28.600
I'm telling you,
we could lose Adele Group this way.

00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:31.770
I'm desperate enough to find in-laws
who will back him up.

00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:34.810
If you're worried,
you should stop causing trouble.

00:15:34.810 --> 00:15:35.810
I warned you.

00:15:35.810 --> 00:15:37.740
It won't be Kim Myung Hui...

00:15:37.740 --> 00:15:39.640
but your own temper
that will get you.

00:15:39.710 --> 00:15:41.480
Get me? Who's going to get me?

00:15:43.280 --> 00:15:45.650
Wait. Did she get me?

00:15:47.350 --> 00:15:48.920
Did I just get played?

00:15:50.950 --> 00:15:52.060
Why that little...

00:15:52.590 --> 00:15:54.560
What? Where are you going?

00:15:55.130 --> 00:15:58.460
What kind of trouble
are you going to start now?

00:16:03.800 --> 00:16:04.840
Darn it!

00:16:14.380 --> 00:16:16.650
Ta-da. Happy birthday, Min Jun.

00:16:23.250 --> 00:16:25.160
I wanted to be the first
to say happy birthday.

00:16:27.090 --> 00:16:30.530
Baek Jin Ju again?
She always gets in my way.

00:16:32.530 --> 00:16:34.670
She should've just stayed in the US.

00:16:34.670 --> 00:16:36.370
Why did she have to come back?

00:16:38.840 --> 00:16:42.440
Why did it have to be
the guy I like? Why?

00:17:01.290 --> 00:17:02.560
He came back out...

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:05.230
instead of spending his birthday
with his family.

00:17:08.570 --> 00:17:11.070
Doesn't his family
celebrate his birthday?

00:17:13.240 --> 00:17:14.440
Just as I thought.

00:17:14.910 --> 00:17:17.270
I'm glad I picked this up,
even if it was last minute.

00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:19.380
Ta-da!

00:17:21.350 --> 00:17:23.250
I made it myself.

00:17:24.280 --> 00:17:26.180
I see. It shows.

00:17:27.520 --> 00:17:31.660
I know it looks a little weird,
but it's good. Here, try it.

00:17:36.430 --> 00:17:37.900
It's pretty good.

00:17:38.200 --> 00:17:39.200
Really?

00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:42.270
I guess when in doubt,
you just throw everything in.

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:44.600
- You threw in everything?
- All right.

00:17:44.600 --> 00:17:46.640
Next up, seaweed soup.

00:17:47.910 --> 00:17:49.310
I've never baked before,

00:17:49.310 --> 00:17:51.540
but I make great seaweed soup,
I swear.

00:18:02.090 --> 00:18:03.750
You're right. It's delicious.

00:18:03.750 --> 00:18:06.190
See? Okay, next.

00:18:06.260 --> 00:18:07.290
There's more?

00:18:11.130 --> 00:18:12.600
Listening
to the birthday song together.

00:18:18.600 --> 00:18:22.640
Happy birthday to you

00:18:22.840 --> 00:18:26.510
Happy birthday to you

00:18:27.240 --> 00:18:30.210
Happy birthday, dear Jin Ju

00:18:30.210 --> 00:18:31.980
On my ninth birthday...

00:18:32.880 --> 00:18:36.190
Happy birthday to you

00:18:36.190 --> 00:18:39.360
My mom recorded this for me
before she passed away.

00:18:43.490 --> 00:18:45.830
It's been my own little tradition...

00:18:45.830 --> 00:18:47.530
to listen to it alone
on my birthday,

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:52.300
but this year,
I wanted to share it with you.

00:18:57.310 --> 00:18:58.410
I just felt like my mom...

00:18:58.410 --> 00:19:00.910
would've wanted to wish you
a happy birthday too.

00:19:02.250 --> 00:19:06.780
She'd say, "It's amazing you share
a birthday with my Jin Ju."

00:19:12.290 --> 00:19:14.260
Thanks for the birthday wishes,
Mother.

00:19:18.660 --> 00:19:21.230
From now on, we'll listen
to it together every year.

00:19:21.970 --> 00:19:24.600
It breaks my heart
to think of you listening...

00:19:25.900 --> 00:19:27.670
to this beautiful song alone.

00:19:30.940 --> 00:19:32.040
It breaks your heart?

00:19:32.580 --> 00:19:33.580
How so?

00:19:34.040 --> 00:19:36.450
Because ten-year-old Jin Ju
must've been crying all by herself.

00:19:41.820 --> 00:19:44.720
I wish we'd met
in elementary school.

00:19:47.020 --> 00:19:48.330
If we'd met back then,

00:19:48.330 --> 00:19:51.230
you probably would've called me
a big crybaby.

00:19:51.560 --> 00:19:52.560
No way.

00:19:54.500 --> 00:19:56.600
No matter when or how
we might have met,

00:19:58.070 --> 00:19:59.500
I would've still fallen for you.

00:20:03.210 --> 00:20:04.210
Hey.

00:20:05.540 --> 00:20:08.680
Did you just tell me
how you feel about me?

00:20:09.350 --> 00:20:11.620
What? It wasn't that.

00:20:11.620 --> 00:20:13.280
It wasn't?

00:20:13.280 --> 00:20:14.750
- What?
- What?

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:16.650
No, that's not what I meant.

00:20:23.030 --> 00:20:25.730
This is kind of awkward
and embarrassing,

00:20:30.070 --> 00:20:32.070
but from the moment I saw you
in the lecture hall,

00:20:36.070 --> 00:20:38.180
I knew I was going to fall for you.

00:20:40.940 --> 00:20:41.950
Me too.

00:20:44.680 --> 00:20:48.120
I liked you from the moment
I first saw you too.

00:20:50.590 --> 00:20:52.620
It felt like I'd known you...

00:20:53.260 --> 00:20:55.560
for a very long time.

00:21:22.420 --> 00:21:24.050
The VIP event went well,

00:21:24.050 --> 00:21:26.320
and Oh Jung Ran got put
in her place.

00:21:26.490 --> 00:21:29.360
You should go
wish Min Jun a happy birthday.

00:21:29.360 --> 00:21:30.360
Sure.

00:21:36.100 --> 00:21:37.370
Hey, Kim Myung Hui!

00:21:41.410 --> 00:21:42.470
It was you, wasn't it?

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:45.680
You used the employee
to set me up, right?

00:21:48.210 --> 00:21:49.210
Why, you...

00:21:50.580 --> 00:21:52.320
Did you just step back?
You little...

00:21:52.850 --> 00:21:54.550
What are you accusing her of?

00:21:54.690 --> 00:21:56.950
You stay out of this.

00:21:57.150 --> 00:21:59.260
Stay out of this, darn it!

00:21:59.720 --> 00:22:01.860
Are you kidding me?

00:22:23.810 --> 00:22:25.450
Who are you to butt in?

00:22:26.180 --> 00:22:27.980
Do you two
know each other or something?

00:22:54.380 --> 00:22:56.810
I'm Baek Jun Gi, CEO of Temi Bio.

00:22:56.910 --> 00:22:59.250
If you happen to need a witness,

00:22:59.820 --> 00:23:00.820
please contact me.

00:23:01.790 --> 00:23:04.790
It seems like
you were being treated unfairly.

00:23:06.120 --> 00:23:07.790
Please, make sure you call.

00:23:08.360 --> 00:23:09.930
I'm sure I can help.

00:23:22.670 --> 00:23:23.670
What?

00:23:23.870 --> 00:23:25.680
A witness? An injustice?

00:23:25.940 --> 00:23:28.210
What did I even do?

00:23:29.710 --> 00:23:31.110
As if you don't know.

00:23:31.820 --> 00:23:33.780
You caused a scene
at an important event...

00:23:33.780 --> 00:23:35.620
and tried to assault me.

00:23:36.190 --> 00:23:38.620
Should I report this to the chairman
exactly as it happened?

00:23:40.560 --> 00:23:41.760
Why you...

00:23:41.760 --> 00:23:43.760
Jung Ran!

00:23:44.830 --> 00:23:45.830
Jung Ran, please.

00:23:46.160 --> 00:23:47.600
Cause any more trouble,

00:23:47.600 --> 00:23:49.600
and you'll be thrown out for good.

00:23:49.770 --> 00:23:51.270
If you're going to start something,

00:23:51.270 --> 00:23:53.570
can we not do it today?

00:23:55.310 --> 00:23:57.670
This isn't over.

00:23:58.040 --> 00:23:59.810
I won't let you get away with this.

00:24:00.110 --> 00:24:03.180
Come on, let's go.

00:24:03.250 --> 00:24:05.650
All right. Off you go.

00:24:12.990 --> 00:24:14.460
(Temi Bio, CEO Baek Jun Gi)

00:24:18.900 --> 00:24:21.430
(Adele Group)

00:24:22.070 --> 00:24:23.570
What are the odds?

00:24:23.630 --> 00:24:24.770
(Temi Bio, CEO Baek Jun Gi)

00:24:24.840 --> 00:24:26.670
I freaked out,
thinking I'd been caught.

00:24:27.800 --> 00:24:30.970
The doctor knew what was going on
but played along to help you.

00:24:32.180 --> 00:24:33.480
So, what are you going to do?

00:24:34.410 --> 00:24:36.280
Are you going to see him again?

00:24:37.780 --> 00:24:40.520
It seemed like
he had something important to say.

00:24:40.820 --> 00:24:42.090
I want to see him again.

00:24:42.850 --> 00:24:45.060
Isn't that way too risky?

00:24:46.260 --> 00:24:49.690
Oh Jung Ran and Chairman Park
are watching your every move.

00:24:50.630 --> 00:24:52.260
How are you going to explain it...

00:24:53.460 --> 00:24:55.730
when they catch you
meeting the doctor?

00:24:56.670 --> 00:24:57.670
If your cover is blown,

00:24:57.670 --> 00:25:00.440
all your work will be for nothing.

00:25:01.870 --> 00:25:05.010
I just need to find somewhere
we can meet in private.

00:25:11.410 --> 00:25:12.880
(Ihwachae Hanbok)

00:25:14.850 --> 00:25:15.850
Ihwachae?

00:25:17.820 --> 00:25:19.560
Not everyone is allowed inside,

00:25:19.560 --> 00:25:21.490
so we could meet in private.

00:25:23.460 --> 00:25:24.460
Please hurry and set it up.

00:25:25.500 --> 00:25:26.500
I'm on it.

00:25:44.180 --> 00:25:45.280
You're home late.

00:25:45.620 --> 00:25:47.520
I had something urgent to attend to.

00:25:48.490 --> 00:25:50.990
I'll head to my room, then.

00:25:51.860 --> 00:25:52.860
Myung Hui.

00:25:56.330 --> 00:25:57.330
Come...

00:25:57.730 --> 00:25:59.100
to my room tonight.

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:04.200
All right.

00:26:04.730 --> 00:26:06.340
That was fast.

00:26:08.910 --> 00:26:11.940
Did you already know
my wife wasn't home?

00:26:16.380 --> 00:26:20.380
I never told you
she'd moved to the annex.

00:26:21.990 --> 00:26:24.050
Your wife came to see me.

00:26:24.750 --> 00:26:28.460
I knew because she accused me
of having her sent to the annex.

00:26:30.790 --> 00:26:31.800
Is that so?

00:27:08.200 --> 00:27:10.430
- Oh.
- Hey.

00:27:11.400 --> 00:27:13.570
Are you just getting home?
It's pretty late.

00:27:14.170 --> 00:27:16.670
I was out celebrating my birthday
with a friend.

00:27:18.210 --> 00:27:21.110
- How was your business trip?
- It was good.

00:27:21.580 --> 00:27:25.320
I meant to get here earlier
for dinner. I'm sorry.

00:27:26.180 --> 00:27:27.180
It's okay.

00:27:31.490 --> 00:27:33.090
Happy birthday.

00:27:33.090 --> 00:27:34.720
I say it every year,

00:27:34.960 --> 00:27:37.790
but I'm so grateful
you were born safe and healthy.

00:27:38.500 --> 00:27:40.130
I'm thankful too, Mother.

00:27:42.300 --> 00:27:43.970
Of course. That's my boy.

00:27:45.500 --> 00:27:47.740
So, Mother...

00:27:51.910 --> 00:27:53.540
Nevermind. It's nothing.

00:27:54.380 --> 00:27:55.780
You should get some rest.

00:27:57.450 --> 00:27:59.320
- Okay, head on up.
- Sure.

00:28:04.490 --> 00:28:05.490
Myung Hui,

00:28:06.460 --> 00:28:08.020
Min Jun's grown up so much,
hasn't he?

00:28:09.830 --> 00:28:11.900
The son you protected
until the very end.

00:28:12.900 --> 00:28:14.660
I'll protect him
to the very end too.

00:28:16.200 --> 00:28:19.670
I'm going to make our Min Jun
the head of the Adele Group.

00:28:24.670 --> 00:28:26.740
Ihwachae is all set.

00:28:37.020 --> 00:28:39.860
There's nowhere to put this down.

00:28:40.360 --> 00:28:41.560
What's with this table?

00:28:41.960 --> 00:28:44.760
It was just as cramped last year.
Nothing's changed.

00:28:45.900 --> 00:28:48.000
I bought the biggest and best one.

00:28:48.230 --> 00:28:51.330
This happens
because you keep telling me...

00:28:51.400 --> 00:28:52.400
to make more food.

00:28:52.700 --> 00:28:56.310
Is this a memorial service
or a banquet?

00:28:56.940 --> 00:28:59.010
Things have been getting better,
all thanks to Dan Hui.

00:28:59.080 --> 00:29:01.240
It's only right
that we do more for Myung Hui.

00:29:01.980 --> 00:29:02.980
That settles it.

00:29:02.980 --> 00:29:06.550
Next year, I'll have
a massive one custom-made.

00:29:06.620 --> 00:29:09.150
Sure, but the table
will still be just as cramped.

00:29:09.590 --> 00:29:10.590
The bigger the table,

00:29:10.590 --> 00:29:13.160
the more food you'll make me cook.

00:29:15.360 --> 00:29:16.590
Not in front of Myung Hui.

00:29:16.960 --> 00:29:19.160
- Hold on. I'm sorry.
- Let's not bicker, okay?

00:29:19.230 --> 00:29:20.460
I'm sorry. It's my fault.

00:29:30.410 --> 00:29:31.410
In the center.

00:29:37.210 --> 00:29:38.920
Dan Hui should be the one here.

00:29:39.520 --> 00:29:40.720
Dan Hui feels...

00:29:40.850 --> 00:29:43.590
too guilty to even visit Myung Hui
at the columbarium.

00:29:44.150 --> 00:29:45.660
Until Myung Hui gets justice,

00:29:45.660 --> 00:29:47.360
the least we can do is step in.

00:29:48.060 --> 00:29:50.230
I'm sure Myung Hui understands.

00:29:50.990 --> 00:29:53.860
She knows what Dan Hui's enduring...

00:29:54.060 --> 00:29:55.060
just to hang on.

00:29:56.170 --> 00:29:58.430
How can life be so cruel?

00:30:00.240 --> 00:30:03.410
My heart breaks
whenever I think of Dan Hui.

00:30:03.970 --> 00:30:04.970
Myung Hui...

00:30:06.440 --> 00:30:08.910
It must break your heart
to see Dan Hui suffering so much.

00:30:09.980 --> 00:30:10.980
So please,

00:30:12.520 --> 00:30:13.720
help our Dan Hui.

00:30:15.350 --> 00:30:16.420
Watch over her.

00:30:19.120 --> 00:30:20.620
Help her get
the justice you deserve...

00:30:21.060 --> 00:30:23.460
so Dan Hui and Min Jun can
finally come see you together.

00:30:25.300 --> 00:30:27.060
Please show her the way.

00:30:43.250 --> 00:30:44.450
What, Ihwachae?

00:30:45.250 --> 00:30:46.780
How did that tramp
get invited there?

00:30:47.280 --> 00:30:49.720
I had someone follow her
at the jewelry event, remember?

00:30:49.890 --> 00:30:51.590
My guy saw her get...

00:30:51.590 --> 00:30:53.290
the Ihwachae gold card himself.

00:30:53.990 --> 00:30:56.590
She got invited to Ihwachae,
when even I couldn't?

00:30:58.360 --> 00:31:01.330
I'm trying to find Hyun Jun a match,
and she's trying to outdo me?

00:31:03.370 --> 00:31:05.070
We're going to Ihwachae. Now.

00:31:06.340 --> 00:31:07.340
What?

00:31:07.400 --> 00:31:09.470
(Ihwachae)

00:31:30.230 --> 00:31:31.790
So we meet again.

00:31:33.900 --> 00:31:36.930
I'm sorry it took all this trouble
just for us to meet.

00:31:37.200 --> 00:31:38.200
That's all right.

00:31:38.800 --> 00:31:41.240
Yoon Jung filled me in
on what happened.

00:31:42.040 --> 00:31:44.010
I should apologize
for insisting on meeting.

00:31:44.570 --> 00:31:45.610
But I did so...

00:31:45.610 --> 00:31:48.280
because there's something
I need to tell you.

00:31:49.380 --> 00:31:52.320
So you did have something
to tell me.

00:31:56.590 --> 00:32:00.620
I have evidence
from the past incident.

00:32:18.610 --> 00:32:21.010
I have it all,
from evidence of the murder...

00:32:21.010 --> 00:32:22.210
to the killer's bloodstains.

00:32:22.980 --> 00:32:24.550
You'll finally be able to prove...

00:32:24.880 --> 00:32:26.680
who killed your sister.

00:33:05.020 --> 00:33:07.960
(Pearl in Red)

00:33:08.260 --> 00:33:12.060
I wish we could
be together like this forever.

00:33:12.160 --> 00:33:14.360
Is Park Min Jun moving to England
to study too?

00:33:14.460 --> 00:33:16.600
Why would you need to study abroad?

00:33:16.600 --> 00:33:17.930
Jin Ju might, but you...

00:33:18.000 --> 00:33:19.400
Jin Ju this, Jin Ju that!

00:33:19.400 --> 00:33:21.600
Dad, why are you always
comparing me to her?

00:33:21.700 --> 00:33:23.940
Why do you always put me down? Why?

00:33:24.240 --> 00:33:26.240
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)